
### Requirements

* kind: https://kind.sigs.k8s.io/
* kubectl
* docker
* Helm: https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/

### Instructions

First, set up a kind cluster, the required Helm charts and the demo pod docker container with this script:

```
$: ./setup.sh
```

Next, launch and login to the demo pod and run the demo script:

```
# Will take a while the first time it is run
$: ./login.sh

# From within the demo pod
$: database-stream-processor/demo/demo.sh
```
